OL,3,CTroublemaker turned hero who helps
OL,4,Chomeless people off the streets
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports' Ellis Nordhoff
OL,7,Fspent the day with teenager Dylan
OL,8,FWilliams who approaches homeless
OL,9,Fpeople to try to find them a place to
OL,10,Fstay.
OL,12,FA 17-year-old who admits he was a
OL,13,Fnuisance to the public is now helping
OL,14,Fhomeless people find housing.
OL,16,FDylan Williams spent much of his
OL,17,Fearlier teenage years on an electric
OL,18,Fbike on the streets of Birkenhead,
OL,19,FWirral, but decided he wanted to give
OL,20,Fback to the community that he felt he
OL,21,Fhad let down.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
