OL,3,CTroublemaker turned hero who helps
OL,4,Chomeless people off the streets
OL,6,FHe now works every day on the streets
OL,7,Fof Merseyside approaching homeless
OL,8,Fpeople and making them known to local
OL,9,Fauthorities to speed up the process of
OL,10,Ffinding a place to stay.
OL,12,FDylan set up Step to Shelter
OL,13,FMerseyside and now has a team of
OL,14,Fvolunteers who join him in his pursuit
OL,15,Fto tackle the housing crisis.
OL,17,FDylan met Joe Fitzpatrick near to the
OL,18,FPyramids Shopping Centre in
OL,19,FBirkenhead, who had been sleeping in
OL,20,Fan abandoned house.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
