OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F395A1752150318
OL,3,CTroublemaker turned hero who helps
OL,4,Chomeless people off the streets
OL,6,FHe added: "My Dad passed away, I just
OL,7,Ffell off the rails a bit. I lost my
OL,8,Fjob, and everything just fell apart.
OL,10,F"They have turned up today and said
OL,11,Fthey are going to get me somewhere to
OL,12,Fstay tonight, and they are going to
OL,13,Fget me a mobile phone.
OL,15,F"Thanks to Dylan today, I appreciate
OL,16,Fit."
OL,18,FDylan realised he wanted to change his
OL,19,Fbehaviour and wanted to do more to
OL,20,Fhelp society, rather than hinder it.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
