OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F395A1752150318
OL,3,CTroublemaker turned hero who helps
OL,4,Chomeless people off the streets
OL,6,FHe said: "I used to drive around on an
OL,7,Felectric bike in a balaclava, getting
OL,8,Finto police chases.
OL,10,F"I'd go into Asda or Tesco and pull
OL,11,Fthe shelves down and make other
OL,12,Fcustomers distressed. I thought that
OL,13,Fwas funny.
OL,15,F"I just thought, I need to stop now
OL,16,Fand I need to support my community and
OL,17,Fnot be against the community.
OL,19,F"That's not normal behaviour and my
OL,20,Fparents didn't bring me up like that."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
