OL,3,CTroublemaker turned hero who helps
OL,4,Chomeless people off the streets
OL,6,FDylan now has a team of volunteers who
OL,7,Fhelp him with his efforts.
OL,9,FOutreach volunteer Colin Weaver said:
OL,10,F"He's got good support around him. But
OL,11,FI don't think he needs it. He's done
OL,12,Feverything on his own really.
OL,14,F"But I think it's good to have older
OL,15,Fpeople around him, because he can
OL,16,Flearn something off us and we can
OL,17,Flearn something off him."
OL,19,FDylan works from 9am-11pm every dayin
OL,20,Fhis pursuit to end homelessness on
OL,21,FMerseyside.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
