OL,3,CTroublemaker turned hero who helps
OL,4,Chomeless people off the streets
OL,6,FStep to Shelter Merseyside now has
OL,7,Fmore than 1500 cases, and has
OL,8,Fsuccessfully helped more than 350
OL,9,Fpeople into temporary accommodation,
OL,10,Fwith some even now living in private
OL,11,Faccommodation.
OL,13,FOnce people are housed, Dylan
OL,14,Fmaintains contact, visiting
OL,15,Findividuals every other week.
OL,17,FHelping one person is not enough, he
OL,18,Fwants to make lasting change in
OL,19,FMerseyside.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
